== Imik n umzruy == 
[[Afaylu:POL lubelskie kurow o001.JPG|thumb|right|200px|Kurow]]
ɣ tusut n isggasn n sdiz idamraw tmun gis yat tamsmunt takalifiniy tamashiyt ɣan ad yi win ay lliɣ gis zdɣn willi mu zwarnin "aytmatn ni polandiyn".

Z ɣu usggas 1660 ar n tini iymzdaɣn n tamdintad aryaniyn lid yuckan ɣ aryus yan talb amasiḥi. talbat ikkatin ɣ misra ɣ tamdint n iskandariya.

ɣu isggas n 1670 tu tamdintad tamadunt n ttaεun, tamaduntad li yas ikkisn atign tamdint turri tga aduwar. Imun ilmma umzruy nes dwin d igmmadn yadinin dis mḥadanin. ɣ usğas 1795 liɣ tbḍa [[Pulunya]] twala [[Namssa]]. Amma ɣ 1809 tmun d varsovya tg ilmma s ɣ tagldit n pulunia z usğ n 1815.

ɣ brayr 1870 tuykkasnas izrfan n tamdint turri tga aduwar. mac ɣ 1918 tkcm d pulunya.

ɣ lgirra tisnat ɣ was n 9 septumbre ḍer tamdintad tk ixrban, ur gis tfil ḥtta sbtar. asğas 1942 tskr gis almanya lḥabs (getto) mac iḥbbasn rad rwln izdern ad alkmn imḥarkan yadnin ɣi idrarn d taganin li ur yagugn.
